{"tid":1201852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[反送中]唔好睇少自己嘅力量先","createTime":"2019-06-11T06:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T07:13:30.000Z","uid":220388,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"52654116b79ead85754d163607f1a2206df4bd53","tid":1201852,"uid":220388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:51:06.000Z","msg":"一個人做到嘅嘢的確唔多，但都唔好抱住放棄嘅狀態。<br />\n就算企唔到出嚟，都可以同身邊嘅人講多啲。<br />\n我身邊嘅同學都係大陸落嚟，起初佢哋都冇點理，但我不斷一有機會就講多啲俾佢哋聽，依家佢哋自願去捐物資，去政總，佢哋甚至已經同咗大陸朋友講解咩係逃犯條例，都想大陸人都可以知多啲呢件事有幾嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n一個人力量細，所以更加要積少成多。<br />\n<br />\n到呢刻，香港人唔應該再沉默，至少要令多啲人知依家發生咩事。<br />\n<br />\n為咗香港 ; 我哋嘅家，有能力嘅就做多幾步啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可以企出嚟嘅，今晚見！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"52ed664e55f3fad27df59654f7187f6492522923","tid":1201852,"uid":220388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:51:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d486dc26a93009426e3ab4996e0e5f01e5ff86f4","tid":1201852,"uid":220388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:07:10.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018f204281de916b27f573624dcc1f6cb373982b","tid":1201852,"uid":220388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:07:31.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae0e488560bdb0b7d382b574774d9acbf1251a2","tid":1201852,"uid":220388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156e2540b741ec404e741daea5b23dd096366486","tid":1201852,"uid":146594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face